# Session [10] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Wireless Infrastructure Topology chist?  (what is the wireless topology is all about?)
- AP che naghshi dar in topology dard? (what is the AP part in this wirless network?)
- Broadcast Domain dar Wireless Infrastructure che kkari anjam mide? ( what do broadcast does in wireless network?)

## Flashback – Infrastructure Basics
- Dar in model → hame device ha be **Access Point (AP)** vasl mishavand 
- AP mishe markaz network wireless  
- Device ha be ham dastaresi daran vali hame traffic az AP miborad  

## Explanation

### Wireless Infrastructure Topology
- Laptop, phone, PC → hame be AP vasl mishavand  
- AP → be switch ya router vasl ast  
- In topology mashhoor-tarin model wireless ast (Wi-Fi khaneh, office, school)  
- Device be device mostaghiman vasl nemishavad → **hame chiz az AP migozarad**

### Broadcast Domain
- Hame device haye vasl shode be hamun AP → **yek broadcast domain**  
- Broadcast az ye device wireless → tamame device haye vasl shode be AP migiran  

### Ussfull word 
- iblss =independent Basic service set {maroff be---> Ad-hoc}
-ess =extended service setcinfrastructurel 

